The '''Ultraball''' is a type of pokeball. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokemon after defeating it if it or a higher type of pokeball is active.


==Details==
===Description===
An excellent pokeball to capture pokemon with. It provides a +10% catch rate bonus.

